Maildrop Host - Edit: Edit Maildrop Host properties
  
  Description

    This view allows you edit the Maildrop Host.

 Controls

    'ID' -- The id of the Maildrop Host.

    'Title' -- The title of the Maildrop Host.

    'Transactional Mode' -- Toggle the Zope transaction-aware mode

    'Maildrop Daemon settings' -- The settings shown in this table
      are read from the file "config.py" in the MaildropHost product
      directory. They are used by the maildrop daemon.
